  "root_text": {
    "iti93:0.1": "Itivuttaka 93 ",
    "iti93:0.2": "Tikanipāta ",
    "iti93:0.3": "Pañcamavagga ",
    "iti93:0.4": "Aggisutta ",
    "iti93:1.1": "Vuttañhetaṁ bhagavatā vuttamarahatāti me sutaṁ: ",
    "iti93:2.1": "“Tayome, bhikkhave, aggī. ",
    "iti93:2.2": "Katame tayo? ",
    "iti93:2.3": "Rāgaggi, dosaggi, mohaggi—",
    "iti93:2.4": "ime kho, bhikkhave, tayo aggī”ti. ",
    "iti93:2.5": "Etamatthaṁ bhagavā avoca. ",
    "iti93:2.6": "Tatthetaṁ iti vuccati: ",
    "iti93:3.1": "“Rāgaggi dahati macce, ",
    "iti93:3.2": "ratte kāmesu mucchite; ",
    "iti93:3.3": "Dosaggi pana byāpanne, ",
    "iti93:3.4": "nare pāṇātipātino. ",
    "iti93:4.1": "Mohaggi pana sammūḷhe, ",
    "iti93:4.2": "ariyadhamme akovide; ",
    "iti93:4.3": "Ete aggī ajānantā, ",
    "iti93:4.4": "sakkāyābhiratā pajā. ",
    "iti93:5.1": "Te vaḍḍhayanti nirayaṁ, ",
    "iti93:5.2": "tiracchānañca yoniyo; ",
    "iti93:5.3": "Asuraṁ pettivisayaṁ, ",
    "iti93:5.4": "amuttā mārabandhanā. ",
    "iti93:6.1": "Ye ca rattindivā yuttā, ",
    "iti93:6.2": "sammāsambuddhasāsane; ",
    "iti93:6.3": "Te nibbāpenti rāgaggiṁ, ",
    "iti93:6.4": "niccaṁ asubhasaññino. ",
    "iti93:7.1": "Dosaggiṁ pana mettāya, ",
    "iti93:7.2": "nibbāpenti naruttamā; ",
    "iti93:7.3": "Mohaggiṁ pana paññāya, ",
    "iti93:7.4": "yāyaṁ nibbedhagāminī. ",
    "iti93:8.1": "Te nibbāpetvā nipakā, ",
    "iti93:8.2": "rattindivamatanditā; ",
    "iti93:8.3": "Asesaṁ parinibbanti, ",
    "iti93:8.4": "asesaṁ dukkhamaccaguṁ. ",
    "iti93:9.1": "Ariyaddasā vedaguno, ",
    "iti93:9.2": "sammadaññāya paṇḍitā; ",
    "iti93:9.3": "Jātikkhayamabhiññāya, ",
    "iti93:9.4": "nāgacchanti punabbhavan”ti. ",
    "iti93:10.1": "Ayampi attho vutto bhagavatā, iti me sutanti. ",
    "iti93:10.2": "Catutthaṁ. "
  },
  "translation_text": {
    "iti93:0.1": "So It Was Said 93 ",
    "iti93:0.2": "The Book of the Threes ",
    "iti93:0.3": "Chapter Five ",
    "iti93:0.4": "Fire ",
    "iti93:1.1": "This was said by the Buddha, the Perfected One: that is what I heard. ",
    "iti93:2.1": "“Mendicants, there are these three fires. ",
    "iti93:2.2": "What three? ",
    "iti93:2.3": "The fires of greed, hate, and delusion. ",
    "iti93:2.4": "These are the three fires.” ",
    "iti93:2.5": "The Buddha spoke this matter. ",
    "iti93:2.6": "On this it is said: ",
    "iti93:3.1": "“The fire of greed burns a mortal, ",
    "iti93:3.2": "lustful, infatuated by sensual pleasures; ",
    "iti93:3.3": "while, fallen in the fire of hate, ",
    "iti93:3.4": "a person kills living creatures; ",
    "iti93:4.1": "and, bewildered by the fire of delusion, ",
    "iti93:4.2": "they miss the teaching of the noble ones. ",
    "iti93:4.3": "Not recognizing these three fires, ",
    "iti93:4.4": "people are caught up in substantial reality. ",
    "iti93:5.1": "They fill the ranks of hell, ",
    "iti93:5.2": "of birth as an animal, ",
    "iti93:5.3": "or of titans and ghosts, ",
    "iti93:5.4": "not freed from Māra’s bonds. ",
    "iti93:6.1": "But as to those committed day and night ",
    "iti93:6.2": "to the teaching of the Buddha: ",
    "iti93:6.3": "they extinguish the fire of greed, ",
    "iti93:6.4": "always perceiving ugliness; ",
    "iti93:7.1": "while those supreme men ",
    "iti93:7.2": "extinguish the fire of hate with love; ",
    "iti93:7.3": "and the fire of delusion with the wisdom ",
    "iti93:7.4": "that leads to penetration. ",
    "iti93:8.1": "Having extinguished these fires, alert, ",
    "iti93:8.2": "tireless all day and night, ",
    "iti93:8.3": "they become fully extinguished, ",
    "iti93:8.4": "completely transcending suffering. ",
    "iti93:9.1": "Seers of the noble truths, knowledge masters, ",
    "iti93:9.2": "the astute, understanding rightly, ",
    "iti93:9.3": "directly know the ending of rebirth, ",
    "iti93:9.4": "they come not back to future lives.” ",
    "iti93:10.1": "This too is a matter that was spoken by the Blessed One: that is what I heard. "
  },
